high_descs: Turn right, go to the sink.
Take the spoon from the right sink.
Turn right, go to the counter to the left of the oven.
Put the spoon in the wine glass on the counter.
Take the wine glass from the counter.
Turn around, go to the white table on the left.
Put the glass on the plate above the bowl on the white table.
anns.task_desc: Put a glass with a spoon on a plate that is on a table.

high_descs: Turn right, then turn left and head over to the sink.
Pick up the spoon from the right side of the sink.
Turn right and place the spoon in the glass in front of you.
Pick up the glass from the counter.
Turn all the way around, so that you're facing the opposite side of the kitchen.
Walk towards the table on your right, and turn to face it.
Place the glass on a plate on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a spoon in a glass, place this glass on a plate.

high_descs: Go to the sink across the room to your right.
Pick up the spoon from the right hand side of the sink.
Go to your right, to the counter to the left of the stove.
Put the spoon into the goblet on the counter, handle side down.
Pick up the goblet, with the spoon in it.
Turn around and go to the table against the wall behind you.
Put the goblet on the center of the large plate on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a goblet holding a spoon in the center of a large plate.
